# Auto Review for Vitest

When editing files matched by this rule:

- Automatically apply `vitest-guidelines` before making or reviewing changes.
- After edits, run `vitest-reviewer` on changed files in scope.
- If changes are substantial, also run `yg-quality-gate`.

## Review expectations

- Prefer deterministic tests (no flaky timing/order dependencies).
- Ensure mocks are reset/restored and async work is awaited.
- Flag committed `it.only`/`describe.only` as blockers.
- Cover error and edge paths, not only happy paths.
